8.2.4 Classification and Depreciation
The accounting treatment for fixed assets differs depending on whether they have been
purchased from programme funds of from the Core/Administration Fund. Fixed Assets
purchased from programme Funds will be expensed in the year of purchase. However a
record of such assets shall be maintained separately at all times in line with clause 8.2.3
above. . Fixed assets bought with core funds or already transferred to SFA Foundation
