research sector on the continent, to raise and uphold standards of safeguarding, building on
existing frameworks and striving for excellence.
l) SFA Foundation in collaboration with its funding partners, will facilitate a dialogue between
research funders, academic and research institutes, private sector and civil society to:
▪ Review existing evidence on safeguarding within the research community on the
continent development research.
▪ Identify and share key aspects of effective practice in prevention and response.
▪ Develop practical and relevant principles and guidance to support universities,
