7.6.3.3 Staff and Staff Resumes
The consultant should give names and backgrounds of those to be working on the
project. Resumes for team leader, support team, thematic experts should also be
included;
7.6.3.4 Cost 20%)
The cost should be reasonable, and commensurate with the time, staff and production
